## Convergence Path

```
{{#each runs}}
Run {{add this.runIndex 1}}: {{this.vus}} VUs → {{#if this.healthy}}HEALTHY{{else}}UNHEALTHY ({{{this.trigger}}}){{/if}}{{#if this.infra}} | CPU: {{this.infra.cpuPeak}} peak{{/if}}
{{/each}}
{{#if hasTippingPoint}}
Result: Tipping point ≈ {{tippingPointVUs}} VUs
{{/if}}
```

### Health Criteria

| Criterion | Threshold |
| --------- | --------- |
| Error Rate | < 1% |
| p95 Latency | < 2,000 ms |
| OOM Kills | 0 |

> **Algorithm:** Exponential growth (double VUs each run) until unhealthy, then binary refinement between last healthy and first unhealthy VU counts. Stops when the search band narrows to the minimum step size or max runs reached.

